        <p>Content on this site is provided for educational and informational purposes. Research publications, dispatches, and data are published under open access. You may share and cite with attribution. Commercial reproduction requires written permission from E5 Enclave Incorporated.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise indicated, all content on this site is the property of E5 Enclave Incorporated or its contributors. The E5 name, logo, and associated marks are trademarks of E5 Enclave Incorporated. This website is built with human-directed design and human-reviewed content.</p>

