        <p>E5 Enclave Incorporated is not liable for any damages arising from the use of this website. This site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.</p>

        <h2>Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida, United States. Disputes shall be resolved in Miami-Dade County, Florida.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms: accounts@e5enclave.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .legal-content { margin-top: var(--s-8); }
    .legal-content h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      margin-top: var(--s-8);
      margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
    }
    .legal-content p {
      color: var(--color-on-surface-secondary);
      margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
      line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
    }
  </style>
